Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拍是喜歡拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我很少看別人拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以嘛
